      "text": [
        " رَأَيْتُ أَبَا جَعْفَرٍ ( عليه السلام ) قَدْ خَفَّفَ لِحْيَتَهُ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "From him, from Usman Bin Isa, from Abdullah Bin Muskan, from Al Hassan Al Zayyat who said, ",
          "‘I saw Abu Ja’far<sup>asws</sup> having lightened his<sup>asws</sup> beard’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "4. It is narrated from the narrator of the previous Hadith from ‘Uthman ibn ‘Isa from ‘Abd Allah ibn Muskan from al-Hassan al-Zayyat who has said the following: “I once saw abu Ja‘far, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, had made his beard lighter.’” "
        ]
      }
